---
title: Bulgogi Pork and Mushroom Stir-Fry with Basmati Rice
description: We love good Pork & Mushroom Stir Fry with Rice and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bulgogi-pork-and-mushroom-stir-fry-c4dfe765-3dc1e868.jpg
